
Select the first element of a specific type
:first-of-type
Selects the first element of that type within another element.


Example --->>> Select first apple

            <div class="table">
            <orange class="small" />
            <apple />
            <apple class="small" />
            <apple />
            <apple class="small" />
            <plate>
            <orange class="small" />
            <orange />
            </plate>
            </div>


ans --->>> apple:first-of-type
